Quick install guide
1) copy tcpdump.hack in /usr/local/bin or somewhere else in your path

2) install maxmind C library and python library
 http://www.maxmind.com/download/geoip/api/c/GeoIP-latest.tar.gz
 http://www.maxmind.com/download/geoip/api/python/GeoIP-Python-latest.tar.gz

3) download db GeoIPASNum.dat and copy it in /usr/local/share/GeoIP
        http://geolite.maxmind.com/download/geoip/database/asnum/GeoIPASNum.dat.gz

4) In a debian-like system run:
        sudo apt-get install gnuplot python-gnuplot python-qt4 python-qt4-dev qt4-dev-tools python-geoip python-qt4-dev pyqt4-dev-tools python-scipy traceroute

5) run `make' in the main p2pgauge directory to build the GUI.
   Remember to run make after modification of the GUI with qt-designer!

6) see README.txt for usage
